Add @minced garlic{2%tbsp} and @minced ginger{2%tbsp} @ground tumeric{1%tsp}, @ground cumin{1%tsp}, @ground coriander{1%tsp}, @chilli powder{1%tsp}, @curry powder{2%tsp}, @garam masala{1%tsp}, @salt{1%tsp}, @black pepper{1/2%tsp}

